  <summary>Make flashcards in your notes</summary>
  <description>
    <p>**Note: This is a community package of RemNote. It is not verified by, affiliated with, or supported by RemNote Inc.**</p>
    <p>RemNote is an all-in-one learning tool that combines note-taking, knowledge management, flashcards, and spaced repetition to enable effective and efficient learning.</p>
    <p>Key features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Notes, Docs &amp; Outlines: Capture and link ideas for long-term knowledge management</li>
      <li>Smart Flashcards: Create flashcards directly from your notes</li>
      <li>Spaced Repetition: Build long-term memory with proven study intervals</li>
      <li>Linked References: Review all notes connected to a topic with contextual links</li>
      <li>PDF Annotation: Highlight, annotate, and create flashcards from documents</li>
      <li>Multimedia Embedding: Incorporate videos, documents, and more into notes</li>
      <li>Tags: Organize notes, to-dos, and multimedia materials</li>
      <li>LaTeX Formulas: Create and edit mathematical formulas inline</li>
      <li>Templates: Automate repetitive note-taking tasks</li>
      <li>Code Blocks: Keep programming notes separate from code</li>
      <li>Import &amp; Sync: Bring data from any note-taking app</li>
      <li>Offline Mode: Work without internet connection</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Perfect for students, researchers, and lifelong learners who want to build lasting knowledge while cutting study time in half.</p>
  </description>
